title: HOUR 3 - Aaron Rodgers, Joel Klatt

description:
Colin Cowherd discusses Packers QB Aaron Rodgers future with the team after not ruling out retirement. FOX Sports CFB Analyst Joel Klatt joins Colin to discuss Oklahoma's victory over Oregon, USC Lincoln Riley and more from Bowl Season!
